{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"environment"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV","text":"ViewEnvironment"}],"externalID":"s:17ViewEnvironmentUI0aB11PropagatingPAAE11environment0aB0AEVvp::SYNTHESIZED::c:objc(cs)UIView","extendedModule":"ViewEnvironmentUI","title":"environment","role":"symbol","modules":[{"relatedModules":["ViewEnvironmentUI"],"name":"WorkflowUI"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironment"},{"type":"text","text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy."}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit\/UIView\/environment"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ViewEnvironment","identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/ViewEnvironment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and provide those overrides in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customize(environment:)"},{"type":"text","text":". E.g.:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["func customize(environm